9
00:01:40,050 --> 00:01:42,050
(It is too hard...)

10
00:01:43,080 --> 00:01:47,120
(Please tell me...)

11
00:01:49,759 --> 00:01:52,570
(What to do?)

12
00:01:56,600 --> 00:01:58,660
