23
00:02:53,450 --> 00:02:57,960
(The answer that my heart will only need,)

24
00:02:57,960 --> 00:03:03,060
(It is you. Only you and always you)

25
00:03:04,210 --> 00:03:06,860
(Could not trade for the world)

26
00:03:06,860 --> 00:03:12,090
(With the best thing I have cherish right now)

27
00:03:12,090 --> 00:03:14,970
(And it is you)

28
00:03:14,970 --> 00:03:17,520
(Have never seen no one)

29
00:03:17,520 --> 00:03:22,870
(That’s the best thing that came across me and my heart)

30
00:03:22,870 --> 00:03:26,390
(What should we call it...)

31
00:03:26,390 --> 00:03:28,890
(The place where it’s only ours)

32
00:03:28,890 --> 00:03:31,950
(The place where it’s you and me)

33
00:03:31,950 --> 00:03:35,280
(From now and ever)

34
00:03:37,160 --> 00:03:41,470
(The place where we leave our tears and wounds)

35
00:03:41,470 --> 00:03:46,390
(Cause it is our area)

36
00:03:46,390 --> 00:03:48,880
(And I)

37
00:04:01,920 --> 00:04:02,650
Hey.

38
00:04:03,650 --> 00:04:05,330
Are you feeling better now?

39
