51
00:04:47,080 --> 00:04:49,159
Maybe she was just mad at you.

52
00:04:51,400 --> 00:04:53,040
I don’t think so.

53
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:54,600
I guess...

54
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:57,280
