57
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:08,120
But that was all my fault.

58
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:09,520
What was it about?

59
00:05:09,520 --> 00:05:11,030
Tell me about it now.

60
00:05:11,960 --> 00:05:13,720
Well, She said...

61
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:16,960
I've been ignoring her,

62
00:05:16,960 --> 00:05:19,000
