64
00:05:26,080 --> 00:05:28,390
Maybe what she said was right.

65
00:05:30,680 --> 00:05:32,100
You were on my mind.

66
00:05:33,440 --> 00:05:35,080
Your face never leaves my thoughts.

67
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:47,270
Come on.

68
00:05:48,520 --> 00:05:49,790
What?

69
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:53,280
Isn’t it good that I care about you?

70
00:05:53,280 --> 00:05:55,280
We're about to come back and become best friends,

71
00:05:55,280 --> 00:05:56,960
Best buddies, just like the same.

72
00:05:58,520 --> 00:05:59,720
Ew,

73
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:01,520
Gross.

74
00:06:01,520 --> 00:06:02,520
What the heck?

75
00:06:03,280 --> 00:06:05,320
Your face looks like you're going to throw up.

76
00:06:05,320 --> 00:06:07,400
What? I wasn’t going to throw up or anything.

77
00:06:07,400 --> 00:06:08,400
You did.

78
00:06:08,400 --> 00:06:09,720
I just saw it

79
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:10,720
Your face was like this.

80
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:12,600
Wahl!

81
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:15,050
But you really did that.

82
00:06:15,050 --> 00:06:16,270
You’re unbelievable

83
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:19,040
Whatever.

84
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:21,440
Come, let’s have a toast.

85
00:06:21,440 --> 00:06:23,480
To our friendship, my dear friend.

86
00:06:24,360 --> 00:06:25,360
Dear friend.

87
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:37,120
Alright, we’re here.

88
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:40,190
Take off your shoes first.

89
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:52,040
Hey, don’t go to bed yet.

90
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:53,640
- Go take a shower first.
- So sleepy.

91
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:56,800
Wahl!

92
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:57,920
Get up.

93
00:06:57,920 --> 00:06:59,159
Get up.

94
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:03,200
I’m going to sleep now.

95
00:07:07,080 --> 00:07:09,600
It stinks everywhere, Wahl.

96
00:07:24,640 --> 00:07:25,830
Guy.

97
00:07:27,320 --> 00:07:29,240
Do you realize how cute you are?

98
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:35,760
What’s with you?

99
00:07:35,760 --> 00:07:36,760
I mean it.

100
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:41,720
You’ve always been adorable,

101
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:44,840
and I was the one who wasn’t brave enough

102
00:07:44,840 --> 00:07:46,470
to admit how I felt about you.

103
00:07:49,400 --> 00:07:50,920
My name’s Wahl.

104
00:07:51,640 --> 00:07:53,080
From the first time I saw you,

105
00:07:53,080 --> 00:07:55,480
