106
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:57,200
Drawing me towards you.

107
00:08:02,560 --> 00:08:04,280
I couldn't help but stare at you.

108
00:08:06,960 --> 00:08:09,560
Glad to have you beside me.

109
00:08:26,520 --> 00:08:27,520
What,

110
00:08:28,320 --> 00:08:29,920
You broke up again?

111
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:33,159
It haven't even been two months with this one yet.

112
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:36,960
I don’t see any problem.

113
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:38,480
Breakups are fine.

114
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:39,679
I'd rather come back to you.

115
00:08:42,120 --> 00:08:43,720
Every time you break up with your girl,

116
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:45,790
you always come back to me.

117
00:08:46,720 --> 00:08:47,720
Like every single time.

118
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:55,790
Sometimes, a thought came to my mind

119
00:08:55,790 --> 00:08:57,400
that if I could date you,

120
00:08:57,400 --> 00:08:59,230
then it would be great.

121
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:06,620
But I could only tell myself that you're my friend.

122
00:09:07,360 --> 00:09:09,240
My closest friend.

123
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:10,760
But my heart...

124
00:09:12,680 --> 00:09:14,360
was at a loss for how to feel about you.

125
00:09:16,520 --> 00:09:18,960
I want to be with you.

126
00:09:18,960 --> 00:09:21,200
I don't want to lose you to someone else.

127
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:22,430
Do you understand that?

128
00:09:26,680 --> 00:09:28,080
Wahl.

129
00:09:29,880 --> 00:09:31,600
What the hell are you doing?

130
00:09:33,800 --> 00:09:35,600
I like you.

131
00:09:38,520 --> 00:09:40,160
Hey.

132
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:35,280
Goodbye, Guy.

133
00:10:53,470 --> 00:10:54,390
(Tew)

134
00:11:27,280 --> 00:11:28,750
I had to do it.

135
00:12:24,040 --> 00:12:25,860
You've challenged me yourself.

136
00:12:27,040 --> 00:12:29,150
Don't make such a shocked face.

137
00:12:30,920 --> 00:12:32,960
Are you going to kill me?

138
00:12:32,960 --> 00:12:34,720
Otherwise, you wouldn't have woken me up, right?

139
00:12:34,720 --> 00:12:35,800
You know

140
00:12:35,800 --> 00:12:38,920
I'd never snuck up on anyone.

141
00:12:38,920 --> 00:12:40,200
I want you to know

142
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:43,240
that I'm the one who's taking your life.

143
00:12:46,680 --> 00:12:48,920
Why did you do this to me?

144
00:12:48,920 --> 00:12:51,040
Even though I saved your life.

145
00:12:51,040 --> 00:12:52,480
Don't you know anything at all?

146
00:12:52,480 --> 00:12:54,280
Haven’t you known

147
00:12:54,280 --> 00:12:57,800
How long I had to put up with other people's abuse?

148
00:12:57,800 --> 00:12:59,640
Have you never known anything?

149
00:13:26,600 --> 00:13:28,920
I’ve already told you.

150
00:13:28,920 --> 00:13:31,440
Go and collect all of the money...

151
00:13:31,440 --> 00:13:32,440
in full.

152
00:13:42,280 --> 00:13:43,280
Yes, Boss.

153
00:13:46,320 --> 00:13:48,000
Can you stop being fucking nosy for once?

154
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:50,280
I believe that if we can seize that area,

155
00:13:50,280 --> 00:13:52,320
Then we’ll be able to expand our territory.

156
00:13:59,560 --> 00:14:01,320
Learn to be more like Tew.

157
00:14:07,600 --> 00:14:10,720
I had to deal with people pushing me around for a long time,

158
00:14:10,720 --> 00:14:13,080
but you get to enjoy being loved?

159
00:14:13,080 --> 00:14:15,760
Do you know how much suffering I've had

160
00:14:15,760 --> 00:14:17,800
since my life ended up this way?

161
00:14:18,760 --> 00:14:20,440
If you have a grudge against me,

162
00:14:20,440 --> 00:14:21,920
You take it out on me.

163
00:14:21,920 --> 00:14:23,160
Why did it to others?

164
00:14:23,160 --> 00:14:24,640
I’ve already done it!

165
00:14:32,680 --> 00:14:35,340
Letting you die a quick death is too simple.

166
00:14:36,160 --> 00:14:37,920
How many times did you have to die?

167
00:14:37,920 --> 00:14:40,480
How many times have you had a new life?

168
00:14:40,480 --> 00:14:42,920
All of that resulted from my decision.

169
00:14:42,920 --> 00:14:45,360
Haven't you ever been grateful for that, huh?

170
00:14:46,680 --> 00:14:48,590
Are you really going to kill me?

171
00:14:49,360 --> 00:14:50,840
You sure you can do it?

172
00:14:52,840 --> 00:14:54,030
Enough!

173
00:14:54,960 --> 00:14:56,960
Tew, stop!

174
00:14:59,120 --> 00:15:01,240
I want to end all of this.

175
00:15:01,240 --> 00:15:03,280
I just want to leave my old life behind.

176
00:15:03,280 --> 00:15:05,560
But if you won't leave me alone,

177
00:15:05,560 --> 00:15:07,240
then I can't let you live any longer.

178
00:15:14,320 --> 00:15:16,840
I'm done, Tew.

179
00:15:16,840 --> 00:15:19,000
Please spare me.

180
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:20,560
I'm done.

181
00:15:20,560 --> 00:15:22,200
I won’t bother you again.

182
00:15:22,200 --> 00:15:24,200
I won’t mess with your loved ones.

183
00:15:25,680 --> 00:15:26,880
Tew, I'm sorry.

184
00:15:26,880 --> 00:15:28,040
Sorry.

185
00:15:28,040 --> 00:15:29,040
Please spare me.

186
00:15:29,800 --> 00:15:31,080
Please spare my life

187
00:15:32,240 --> 00:15:33,390
I'm finished.

188
00:15:34,080 --> 00:15:35,160
Tew.

189
00:15:35,160 --> 00:15:36,160
I’m done

190
00:15:36,800 --> 00:15:38,700
I’m really finished.

191
00:15:38,700 --> 00:15:40,760
This is the last time.

192
00:15:40,760 --> 00:15:42,680
I hope this shit finally comes to an end.

193
00:15:42,680 --> 00:15:45,040
Show me your face again

194
00:15:45,040 --> 00:15:46,560
and you’re dead.

195
00:16:00,920 --> 00:16:02,600
I'll stop...

196
00:16:02,600 --> 00:16:05,000
because I have bigger problems than getting revenge.

197
00:16:05,000 --> 00:16:06,000
Tew.

198
00:16:38,120 --> 00:16:39,120
Guy.

199
00:16:46,560 --> 00:16:48,310
I was wondering where you were.

200
00:17:02,600 --> 00:17:03,670
I couldn’t sleep.

201
00:17:15,400 --> 00:17:16,400
Why couldn’t you sleep?

202
00:17:21,800 --> 00:17:25,280
Was it because of what I said last night?

203
00:17:25,280 --> 00:17:27,640
I was very drunk,

204
00:17:27,640 --> 00:17:29,360
so there isn't much I remember.

205
00:17:40,120 --> 00:17:41,640
You said...

206
00:17:43,160 --> 00:17:45,160
You like me...

207
00:17:45,160 --> 00:17:47,290
and always want to be by my side.

208
00:17:48,480 --> 00:17:50,000
Don't you remember?

209
00:17:55,040 --> 00:17:57,600
If you don't know what to answer,

210
00:17:57,600 --> 00:17:59,560
I get it.

211
00:17:59,560 --> 00:18:01,920
You were drunk,

212
00:18:01,920 --> 00:18:03,640
so it was normal to rant.

213
00:18:04,960 --> 00:18:06,670
Go take a shower,

214
00:18:07,560 --> 00:18:09,080
I’ll go get you something to eat.

215
00:18:12,320 --> 00:18:13,350
Guy.

216
00:18:15,680 --> 00:18:16,680
Talk to me.

217
00:18:24,080 --> 00:18:26,920
I also don't know how to deal with my own feelings.

218
00:18:28,840 --> 00:18:30,480
I promise

219
00:18:30,480 --> 00:18:32,040
I’ll never hurt your feelings again.

220
00:18:32,040 --> 00:18:34,600
But please understand me.

221
00:18:34,600 --> 00:18:36,910
These things have never happened to me before.

222
00:18:38,520 --> 00:18:40,480
Some things

223
00:18:40,480 --> 00:18:43,030
