224
00:18:44,280 --> 00:18:46,160
Can you give me some more time?

225
00:18:53,760 --> 00:18:55,760
I need some time too.

226
00:18:59,720 --> 00:19:02,030
I still can’t get over him.

227
00:19:08,400 --> 00:19:10,720
But I’ll always be here for you.

228
00:19:15,560 --> 00:19:17,030
Go take a shower right now.

229
00:19:17,880 --> 00:19:19,600
You’ve woken up

230
00:19:19,600 --> 00:19:21,270
