231
00:19:22,000 --> 00:19:23,750
Your breath probably smells rotten.

232
00:19:24,480 --> 00:19:25,670
Go take a shower.

233
00:19:38,120 --> 00:19:39,640
Here…

234
00:19:39,640 --> 00:19:41,610
